msgid "# Using AISBench"
msgstr "# 使用 AISBench"

msgid ""
"This document guides you to conduct accuracy testing using "
"[AISBench](https://github.com/AISBench/benchmark/tree/master). AISBench "
"provides accuracy and performance evaluation for many datasets."
msgstr ""
"本文档指导您使用 [AISBench](https://github.com/AISBench/benchmark/tree/master) "
"进行精度测试。AISBench 为多个数据集提供精度和性能评估。"

msgid "## Online Server"
msgstr "## 在线服务"

msgid "### 1. Start the vLLM server"
msgstr "### 1. 启动 vLLM 服务"

msgid "You can run docker container to start the vLLM server on a single NPU:"
msgstr "您可以运行 Docker 容器在单张 NPU 上启动 vLLM 服务："

msgid "Run the vLLM server in the docker."
msgstr "在 Docker 中运行 vLLM 服务。"

msgid ""
"`--max-model-len` should be greater than `35000`, this will be suitable for "
"most datasets. Otherwise the accuracy evaluation may be affected."
msgstr "`--max-model-len` 应大于 `35000`，这样适用于大多数数据集。否则精度评估可能会受到影响。"

msgid "The vLLM server is started successfully, if you see logs as below:"
msgstr "如果看到如下日志，则表示 vLLM 服务启动成功："

msgid "### 2. Run different datasets using AISBench"
msgstr "### 2. 使用 AISBench 运行不同数据集"

msgid "#### Install AISBench"
msgstr "#### 安装 AISBench"

msgid ""
"Refer to [AISBench](https://github.com/AISBench/benchmark/tree/master) for details.\n"
"Install AISBench from source."
msgstr ""
"详情请参考 [AISBench](https://github.com/AISBench/benchmark/tree/master)。\n"
"从源码安装 AISBench。"

msgid "Install extra AISBench dependencies."
msgstr "安装额外的 AISBench 依赖。"

msgid "Run `ais_bench -h` to check the installation."
msgstr "运行 `ais_bench -h` 检查安装。"

msgid "#### Download Dataset"
msgstr "#### 下载数据集"

msgid ""
"You can choose one or multiple datasets to execute accuracy evaluation."
msgstr "您可以选择一个或多个数据集来执行精度评估。"

msgid "1. `C-Eval` dataset."
msgstr "1. `C-Eval` 数据集。"

msgid ""
"Take `C-Eval` dataset as an example. You can refer to "
"[Datasets](https://github.com/AISBench/benchmark/tree/master/ais_bench/benchmark/configs/datasets)"
" for more datasets. Each dataset has a `README.md` with detailed download "
"and installation instructions."
msgstr ""
"以 `C-Eval` 数据集为例。更多数据集请参考 "
"[Datasets](https://github.com/AISBench/benchmark/tree/master/ais_bench/benchmark/configs/datasets)。每个数据集都有"
" `README.md` 文件，其中包含详细的下载和安装说明。"

msgid "Download dataset and install it to specific path."
msgstr "下载数据集并安装到指定路径。"

msgid "2. `MMLU` dataset."
msgstr "2. `MMLU` 数据集。"

msgid "3. `GPQA` dataset."
msgstr "3. `GPQA` 数据集。"

msgid "4. `MATH` dataset."
msgstr "4. `MATH` 数据集。"

msgid "5. `LiveCodeBench` dataset."
msgstr "5. `LiveCodeBench` 数据集。"

msgid "6. `AIME 2024` dataset."
msgstr "6. `AIME 2024` 数据集。"

msgid "7. `GSM8K` dataset."
msgstr "7. `GSM8K` 数据集。"

msgid "#### Configuration"
msgstr "#### 配置"

msgid ""
"- `attr`: Identifier for the inference backend type, fixed as `service` (serving-based inference) or `local` (local model).\n"
"- `type`: Used to select different backend API types.\n"
"- `abbr`: Unique identifier for a local task, used to distinguish between multiple tasks.\n"
"- `path`: Update to your model weight path.\n"
"- `model`: Update to your model name in vLLM.\n"
"- `host_ip` and `host_port`: Update to your vLLM server ip and port.\n"
"- `max_out_len`: Note `max_out_len` + LLM input length should be less than `max_model_len`(config in your vllm server), `32768` will be suitable for most datasets.\n"
"- `batch_size`: Update according to your dataset.\n"
"- `temperature`: Update inference argument."
msgstr ""
"- `attr`: 推理后端类型标识符，固定为 `service`（服务化推理）或 `local`（本地模型）。\n"
"- `type`: 用于选择不同的后端 API 类型。\n"
"- `abbr`: 本地任务的唯一标识符，用于区分多个任务。\n"
"- `path`: 更新为您的模型权重路径。\n"
"- `model`: 更新为 vLLM 中的模型名称。\n"
"- `host_ip` 和 `host_port`: 更新为您的 vLLM 服务 IP 和端口。\n"
"- `max_out_len`: 注意 `max_out_len` + LLM 输入长度应小于 `max_model_len`（在 vLLM 服务中配置），`32768` 适用于大多数数据集。\n"
"- `batch_size`: 根据数据集更新。\n"
"- `temperature`: 更新推理参数。"

msgid "#### Execute Accuracy Evaluation"
msgstr "#### 执行精度评估"

msgid "Run the following code to execute different accuracy evaluation."
msgstr "运行以下代码执行不同的精度评估。"

msgid ""
"After each dataset execution, you can get the result from saved files such "
"as `outputs/default/20250628_151326`, there is an example as follows:"
msgstr "每个数据集执行完成后，您可以从保存的文件（如 `outputs/default/20250628_151326`）中获取结果，示例如下："

msgid "#### Execute Performance Evaluation"
msgstr "#### 执行性能评估"

msgid "Text-only benchmarks:"
msgstr "纯文本基准测试："

msgid "Multi-modal benchmarks (text + images):"
msgstr "多模态基准测试（文本 + 图像）："

msgid ""
"After execution, you can get the result from saved files, there is an "
"example as follows:"
msgstr "执行完成后，您可以从保存的文件中获取结果，示例如下："

msgid "### 3. Troubleshooting"
msgstr "### 3. 故障排除"

msgid "#### Invalid Image Path Error"
msgstr "#### 无效图像路径错误"

msgid ""
"If you download the TextVQA dataset following the AISBench documentation:"
msgstr "如果您按照 AISBench 文档下载 TextVQA 数据集："

msgid "you may encounter the following error:"
msgstr "您可能会遇到以下错误："

msgid ""
"You need to manually replace the dataset image paths with absolute paths, "
"changing `/path/to/benchmark/ais_bench/datasets/textvqa/train_images/` to "
"the actual absolute directory where the images are stored:"
msgstr ""
"您需要手动将数据集图像路径替换为绝对路径，将 "
"`/path/to/benchmark/ais_bench/datasets/textvqa/train_images/` "
"更改为图像存储的实际绝对目录："

msgid ""
"Update the file `ais_bench/benchmark/configs/models/vllm_api/vllm_api_general_chat.py`.\n"
"There are several arguments that you should update according to your environment."
msgstr ""
"更新文件 `ais_bench/benchmark/configs/models/vllm_api/vllm_api_general_chat.py`。\n"
"你需要根据环境更新其中的几个参数。"
